			<contents rdf:parseType="Literal"><div xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" lang="en" xml:lang="en">
  <p>In the future, a young boy passes an exam and gets to go to an elite school.  There, he has adventures.</p>
</div></contents>
